txt.en: 'It appears we have reached a dead end... let us look around for clues. Do not be fooled by the inactivity of the spike traps here... just because stepping on these holes does not make the spikes pop out, does not mean they are broken. It is likely they are controlled by another means... something does not feel right about this room. Stay on guard.'
Any advice for me in this location?
I will keep an eye out.
